<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٤٩]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">بَابُ مَا جَاءَ فِي قَوْلِ اللَّهِ تَعَالَى:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{وَلَئِنْ أَذَقْنَاهُ رَحْمَةً مِّنَّا مِن بَعْدِ ضَرَّاءَ مَسَّتْهُ لَيَقُولَنَّ هَذَا لِي}</span> الآيَةَ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c2">«هَذَا بِعَمَلِي، وَأَنَا مَحْقُوقٌ بِهِ»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c2">«يُرِيدُ: مِنْ عِنْدِي»</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c3">{قَالَ إِنَّمَا أُوتِيتُهُ عَلَى عِلْمٍ}</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ قَتَادَةُ:</span> <span class="c2">«عَلَى عِلْمٍ مِنِّي بِوُجُوهِ المَكَاسِبِ»</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُونَ:</span> <span class="c2">«عَلَى عِلْمٍ مِنَ اللَّهِ أَنِّي لَهُ أَهْلٌ»</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَهَذَا مَعْنَى قَوْلِ مُجَاهِدٍ:</span> <span class="c2">«أُوتِيتُهُ عَلَى شَرَفٍ»</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وَعَنْ أَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ رَضِيَ اللهُ عَنْهُ:</span> أَنَّهُ سَمِعَ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>